      outside of tech, i also like to unicycle, ski, and make timelapses. big fan of equitable public
      transport as well.
      <br />
      <span class="py-2">
        i go by <code class="font-mono bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 p-1 mt-1 rounded-sm"
          >@henrikvtcodes</code
        > on most platforms.
      </span>
